Class Checker

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • Checker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable

    public class Checker
extends javax.swing.JComponent
    A component to represent a checker. A checker is either occupialbe or not. Available checkers will be drawn in light background color, while unoccupiable checkers in dark background color. An available checker can be filled with a white or black chess or left empty.
